Description:
Full Observability Stack add karte ho – Monitoring (Prometheus + Grafana) and Logging (Loki).

🛠 Tools Used:

Jenkins

Docker

Kubernetes

Helm

ArgoCD

Prometheus + Grafana (Monitoring)

Loki (Logging)

🏗 Architecture:
Jenkins → Docker Build + Push → Git (Helm chart update)
ArgoCD → Sync → K8s Deploy
Prometheus → Metrics collection
Grafana → Visualization dashboards
